    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106490/extras/cc99fefb3cc8c35244c933df87ea3691.avif?t=1732260244\" width=590 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「片桐同学非常冷淡 」是由日本知名游戏社团プラスカゼット制作，Hanabi games汉化发行的一款RPG游戏。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106490/extras/32ae2b688aa35b8dd87adf6d18a30705.avif?t=1732260244\" width=550 height=70 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一睁眼，自己居然和同班的片桐同学一起被关在了奇怪的房间里，本以为是那种套路的恶作剧密室逃脱，但这个房间越是调查越是让我心里发毛，这到底是怎么回事啊……我和片桐同学到底能不能平安逃出去呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106490/extras/6af218394f383839a665e799730baf6b.avif?t=1732260244\" width=550 height=70 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106490/extras/638641c074cea1071689e2e6d3a8434c.avif?t=1732260244\" width=550 height=380 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106490/extras/a5de8d1155e9332a22fcf30055517993.avif?t=1732260244\" width=550 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jrpg</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解谜逃脱</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷人的故事剧情</p></li></ul>",
